ase pressure and plea negotiation demonstrates solid research and careful analysis."-Michigan Law Review  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Aug 2020) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUChP eBook-Package Archive 1960-1989z978311066784440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226778242423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780226778242.jpg  a978-3-11-066784-4  UChP eBook-Package Archive 1960-1989c1960d1989  aGBV-deGruyter-alles